==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ultra vires
<hw>Ul`tra vi"res</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <ety>[Law Latin, from L. prep.
<ets>ultra</ets> beyond + <ets>vires</ets>, pl. of. <ets>vis</ets>
strength.]</ety> <def>Beyond power; transcending authority; -- a phrase
used frequently in relation to acts or enactments by corporations in
excess of their chartered or statutory rights.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ultrazodiacal</ent>⟦br⟧
